\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b1\i0\cf1 Here, vigram is kind of saying the opposite -an artist is excess. No. An artist is emptiness.}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b1\i0\cf1 VIGRAM NEEDS TO SAY-\loch\af3\hich\af3\dbch\af3\uc1\u8220\'93BEFORE I SAID ARTIST IS ABOUT EXCESS. THIS WAS FALSE. ITS ABOUT EMPTINESS.}
